## Germplasm Phenotype:
   - [ipgam1-1 ipgam2-2]()&nbsp;---&nbsp;Vegetative and reproductive growth are greatly reduced with respect to wild type. Pale reticulate leaf phenotype.  Double mutants are self-sterile due to failure to produce pollen grains.
